{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_11", "eventName": "淬火塵霾", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "11-1", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "維護榮耀", "storyInfo": "二十六年前，坎伯蘭公爵府舉辦的一場宴會上，國王與貴族們齊聚一堂，維多利亞國劍諸王之息失蹤的消息傳來。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十六年前"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "1072年"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "5:11 P.M. 天氣/陰"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆奧克特里格區，坎伯蘭公爵府"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g11_lentinobleroom_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 1.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 陛下......我剛剛收到消息，那兩名可憐的議員已經死在獄中。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是他們應得的下場。是時候讓議會明白，他們該服務的對象是維多利亞，而不是拼命向他們兜裡塞金幣的大商人。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我理解您的急切。然而，有人擔憂，您對法院的施壓嚇壞了許多原本還在觀望的議員，他們接下來也許會舉措失當。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 他們就該感到恐懼！這會讓他們更好地認清自己的位置。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 接連而來的戰爭消耗著我們的祖先世代積累的財富，卻將某些貪婪的羽鷲餵養得腦滿腸肥。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我並非想勸您退讓，可要是能慢一些......", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 慢一些！羽鷲從來不懂得適可而止。你怎麼不勸它們搶食的時候慢一些？", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 倘若我們不繼續推行新的稅收政策，到了敵人想要撲上來撕扯維多利亞的血肉的時候，就連傭兵都會離我們而去！", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 只要是神志清醒，又有著廉恥之心的將士，都會站在您身邊。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 在被迫分出半頂王冠之前，紅龍恐怕也是這麼想的。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 他的結局我們都看到了。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我向您保證，在任何時刻，您都將擁有坎伯蘭的忠誠。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 當然，“永遠高潔的坎伯蘭”——我怎麼可能懷疑你的立場？", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 可是羅伯特，維多利亞已經到了真正危急的時刻。在這片土地上，國王的權威正在與日俱減。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 陛下，您為何會這麼想？", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 後天就是您的誕辰，大家都盼望著看到您的身姿，軍人們都急著向您敬禮，民眾的歡呼聲也一定會淹沒閱兵場。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 今年也許會。但明年呢？等到我的亞歷山德莉娜繼位時又會如何？", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 羅伯特，我們終會離去，或遲或早。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 陛下！您——", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 陛下，公爵閣下。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 請原諒我擅作主張的打擾，我剛剛收到報告——", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 王宮地下遭到了入侵，諸王之息下落不明。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......什麼？", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 並且......亞歷山德莉娜殿下也下落不明。", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 衛隊已經封鎖了相關區域，搜索也在進行中，可暫時還沒有線索......", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 在現在這麼敏感的局勢下，亞歷山德莉娜殿下和國劍一起失蹤？", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不，任何貴族都還不至於如此明目張膽，可......", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 陛下，請您放心，我會親自負責這件事，我馬上就......", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不必慌張，我的老朋友。亞歷山德莉娜有她的老師相伴，我相信沒有人能威脅她的安全。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 老師？您是說......", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 他對亞歷山德莉娜很好，我甚至不記得他曾對我展露過同等程度的關切。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 至於我們的諸王之息，無論它在何處，都會盡到它的本分。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 您的意思是......國劍的本分？", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 呵，在被那些老學究反覆研究之前，被具有德行的君王持握在手，才是國劍的意義。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們都期待著那一天的到來。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我明白了。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 羅伯特，為了我們各自的女兒。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 是，陛下......也為了維多利亞。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g2_dukegarden", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 請等一下，小姐，別跑那麼快——", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那不行，艾爾希，我得去找父親！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我知道他今天在家裡，要是我跑得不夠快的話，他就又要跑到不知道哪裡去啦！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#10$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵大人最近很忙，可要是他知道您在找他的話，一定願意花時間陪陪您。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我不要他陪我！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您急著去見他是為了......", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我......我要同他說清楚，我不想去約克郡。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不喜歡鄉下嗎？那裡的莊園比這裡的宅子要寬敞得多，您以前可喜歡那片草地了，還總是拉著佃戶的孩子一塊玩板球。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我是很喜歡那個地方！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#8$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 可明明還沒到夏天，往常這時候我們都還是待在倫蒂尼姆。再說了，這次只有我和媽媽去，你不覺得很奇怪嗎？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您先別著急。我聽曼徹斯特伯爵府的管家說，今年有許多貴族家的少爺小姐提前去鄉下避暑。搞不好是什麼社交界的新潮流呢？", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 才不是呢。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 艾爾希，爸爸在躲著我。他要趕我走，這到底是為什麼呀？是因為我總要他教我練劍，還是我高盧語總學不好，所以他生氣了？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛小姐，或許我不該說下面的話......", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這裡沒有禮儀老師，我才不管你該說什麼又不該說什麼呢。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#2$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我只能說說自己看見的。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小姐，公爵大人很愛您。不管他做了什麼決定，他都是為了您與夫人好。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 為了我好的話，他就更不應該把我送走。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我......我會想他的。很想很想。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#10$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......瞧您，怎麼不好意思了起來？", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 因為只有小孩子才這麼說話！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#8$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我不想讓爸爸覺得我離不開他，我應該再堅強一點，這樣的話，我就能早點當上騎士，就像曾曾曾曾祖母一樣——", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可您本來就還是個孩子呀。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您該試著把自己心裡想的都告訴公爵大人。他是一位溫和寬厚的好公爵，也是一名善解人意的好父親，一定能理解您的想法。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那你同意我去找他了？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我永遠支持您的決定。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，您至少留意著腳下，別被花草絆倒了，否則園丁吉姆又會因為弄傷您而羞愧得吃不下飯。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 告訴吉姆，他養的花草能弄傷我的話，那可是他的本事！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#3$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，真是拿您沒辦法。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "千萬小心您的裙子，阿勒黛小姐......等晚宴開始，您還得覲見陛下啊！", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_manorindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 您見到那位查爾斯·林奇了嗎？", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新受封的蒸汽騎士......以他的年紀，是多麼了不起的成就。今天一定有許多人是衝著他來的。", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 可惜他沒有待多久就匆匆離開了。我聽說所有駐紮在倫蒂尼姆的蒸汽騎士都同時收到了調令。", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這一回是薩爾貢還是萊塔尼亞？", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天佑維多利亞，可別再打仗了，每結束一場戰爭，我就得多賣掉幾幅祖父留下來的畫。物價漲得太快啦。", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這一次是來自議會的直接調令。", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......議會？", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，當然......蒸汽騎士本就隸屬於議會。您的消息總是那麼靈通。", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 掌握更多資訊才能更好地投資，特別是在如今。這可不僅僅是賺來或者虧掉多少鎊的問題。", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們在決定這個國家的未來，正因如此，才得多認識些有識之士。", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 林奇少校......", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該稱他為查爾斯爵士了。", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......查爾斯爵士是一位正直勤勉的好騎士，他忠誠於我們的國家，忠誠於維多利亞。", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 他在北部邊境領的高速戰艦上駐守了近十年，立下戰功無數，眼下還這麼年輕，就已經被拔擢為蒸汽騎士，真是前途不可限量啊。", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說他以前也生活在倫蒂尼姆，好像就在奧克特里格區？我倒是沒聽說過關於他家人的消息。", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 無論他的家人是做什麼的，他都是維多利亞的棟樑之材。", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 如今能獲得殊榮成為蒸汽騎士的，早已不是過去那些圍在陛下身邊只會諂媚的近臣。", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這話似乎意有所指？", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不不不，我可不敢。只是有查爾斯爵士珠玉在側，某些靠著祖上榮耀維繫至今的人，就相形見絀啦——", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_176", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 250.0, "power": 16.0, "times": 2.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "power": 16.0, "times": 2.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "jump", "xpos": 50.0, "power": 15.0, "times": 2.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_176", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哎呦......這是誰家的孩子？怎麼在宴會廳裡橫衝直撞的？萬一驚擾到陛下與公爵大人，可是要被抓起來的！", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這身裙裝......還有髮色......理查，她是......", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 坎伯蘭一家才不是只會諂媚！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#4$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們配得上蒸汽甲胄！我們會為了陛下和維多利亞衝鋒陷陣，獻出生命！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#4$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 阿勒黛小姐！", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 萬分抱歉，勳爵大人，瑪莎女士......小姐只是身體不適，無意對客人們失禮。我本該帶她去休息，這是我的過失。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 艾爾希，這怎麼會是你的過失？！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 坎伯蘭一家的榮耀，決不許任何人玷污！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#4$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我也會像我的先祖一樣，成為偉大的蒸汽騎士的！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 等我長大了......我，我會證明給你們所有人看！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#4$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 小姐！", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 打擾了。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#7$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 唉，您慢些！", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 大人，女士，我得去找阿勒黛小姐。請容我告退。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的這位阿勒黛小姐倒是個心直口快的好孩子。", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 呵呵......本以為要到晚宴的時候才有機會見到阿勒黛小姐，我們也很幸運，是不是啊，瑪莎？", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 孩子們總是有天真無邪的資本的。可不管是誰......", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 都得學著長大。", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛氣喘吁吁地跑了很長一段路。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她本來應該去找父親，她也不知道為什麼鑽進了這個小房間。這裡離宴會廳和公爵的書房都很遠，差不多快到閣樓了。"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能是因為她正在氣頭上。她不理解爸爸為何要趕走她，更不理解那些衣著華貴的客人為什麼要這麼說坎伯蘭。"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每次她遇到生活上的不如意，比如輸了板球比賽，或者她的公爵父親錯過了她的生日宴會，她都會來這裡，找她的老朋友說說話。"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "32_i15", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 他們都忘了，您才是最厲害的蒸汽騎士！", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 可是，父親教導我，真正勇敢的人不怕犧牲，更不怕被遺忘......所以我不該與他們爭辯的。", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我真想快點長大......然後也成為一名最光榮的蒸汽騎士，把我們的敵人通通打敗！", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我會讓那些說坎伯蘭家壞話的人一個個都羞得抬不起頭來！", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 大概我是做不到您那麼厲害啦。不過，要是我能有二分之一，不，三分之二個您這麼厲害，也就滿足了。", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 唔，不過父親說過，身為坎伯蘭家族的人，必須得擁有最高遠的目標！那麼......", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 您會督促我的，是嗎？當然，我也不會輸給您！", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " （......有人來了？！）", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#5$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " （是艾爾希嗎？）", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#5$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她並不想這麼快就被抓回宴會廳，於是她貓著腰，一步躥到了熟悉的蒸汽甲胄後面。"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殘缺的甲胄就像保護著自己年幼的後代一樣，將她嬌小的身體完全罩了起來。"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陌生的腳步聲逐漸靠近。"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "視線被盔甲阻擋了大半，阿勒黛並不能看清他們的臉，只能瞥見兩道變形的影子。"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 時間緊迫，機會難得，我們必須確認一些事。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你確定這裡很安全？", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個角落很偏僻。其他賓客都還在宴會廳，沒人注意到我們離開。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，有人注意到了。"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛心想，不是每個人都喜歡留在金碧輝煌的大廳裡無所事事的。"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不明白。我們為什麼不選在今天動手？獅子好不容易離開他的洞穴，這裡可沒有幾個衛兵。", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一場暗殺並不能解決問題。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別告訴我你害怕絞刑架，長官。", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起你對貧窮的懼怕，絞刑架於我，還是更輕鬆一些的。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我實在厭倦了腦袋和錢包都握在別人手上的日子。勞煩快些動手吧。", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老獅子死了，還有小獅子。王冠依舊穩穩地戴在他們頭頂上，像套牲口一樣套住了我們。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是我們殺得掉一個國王，就能殺掉第二個。", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說得輕鬆。聽好了，我們得有耐心。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒸汽騎士已被全體調離。等他們回到倫蒂尼姆，事情已經塵埃落定。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時候他們會怎麼做？", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和那幾位大人一樣，他們不求私利，一心只為維多利亞。即便不方便支援我們的行動，他們也會理解大人們的決定。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那還剩下皇家衛隊。", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閱兵場......", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......控制住全部塔樓騎士......關鍵是掌握城防軍......", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......有些大公爵早已厭煩了......", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛的臉貼著冰涼的甲胄，可是汗水還是不斷滑過她的額頭。"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保持一動不動變得很困難，外加還要控制呼吸的幅度。兩個影子發出來的聲音漸漸飄遠，又突然來到跟前。"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她打了個激靈，盡力不讓自己的身體露出來，就連腳趾都繃得緊緊的。"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這鐵玩意兒一直在這裡嗎？", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......初代蒸汽騎士的甲胄。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初代？！兩百多年了，它也能算個古董了吧？肯定能賣個好價錢。", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒看到家徽嗎？這是坎伯蘭家的蒸汽甲胄。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它曾經的主人穿著它，站在高盧人的火炮面前，支撐了足足三個小時，就為了讓當時的陛下與一同遭殃的平民全身而退。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打掃戰場的時候，人們才發現，這具甲胄被轟得只剩下一半，裡面的人恐怕早在炮擊開始沒多久時就已經死去——", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——但即使死了，騎士都還是堅持保護著自己的王與同胞，遲遲不願倒下。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有高盧血統的人明明是你，沒想到你比我更喜歡念叨這些大貴族的英勇事蹟。", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我只是對稱得上英雄的人們保有最基本的敬意。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "英雄的遺物不該被你這種眼光打量。就算哪天這座公爵府都化成了灰，坎伯蘭一家也不會捨得變賣這具甲胄。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......該死的貴族的榮譽感，對吧？在我看來毫無意義。", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他大可以和其他大公爵一樣作壁上觀。無論城內名義上的統治者是誰，大公爵的權力都暫時不會受到損害。", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是他能識時務些，他就不是坎伯蘭了。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他為什麼就不能放下自己對獅子的忠誠呢？維多利亞即將迎來巨大的變革，他不如早些認清自己該效忠什麼。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "channel": "slide", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下面怎麼回事？", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有很多士兵突然圍住了公爵府。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？！", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別出聲，仔細聽。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "slide", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "王宮地下......入侵者......", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劍......失竊......", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "封鎖奧克特里格區的主要街道......不得進出......", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽到下面在說什麼了嗎？", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們在找人。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找誰？", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下的衛隊全部出動了。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道他們知道我們在這裡會面......大人，我們該怎麼辦？", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前面傳來了一點輕微的響動，像是有人輕輕歎了口氣。"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛的心怦怦直跳。"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}